               <msContents>
                  <summary>Art roll produced for the tourist industry with icons of Saint George and the Dragon, and Madonna and Child, with excerpts from the text of the Image of Mary, and the Nicean Creed.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="3r" facs="003">Fols 3r and following</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4131Salam">Salām to Jesus
                                                  Christ</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Twelve lines of text: Excerpt from Image of Jesus, poorly copied to fill the space</note>
                </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2"><locus from="5r" facs="005">Fols 5r and following</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3308Nicene">Nicene Creed</title>
                  <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                  <note>Thirteen lines of text: collection of phrases of Gǝ`ǝz from the Nicaean creed and elsewhere, poorly copied to fill the space</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <objectDesc form="Scroll">
                     <supportDesc>
